# Ops dashboard — static UI on the main Ekasi Pay API (ekasi-pay-api).

# Dev: Vite proxies /api → local API (default http://localhost:8787).
# Prod: API_HOST / VITE_API_URL set at build time.

# Ops login (username + password) is handled by the MAIN API:
#   OPS_SUPER_ADMIN_USERNAME=superadmin
#   OPS_DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=your-password
#   (or OPS_SUPER_ADMIN_PASSWORD)
# Set those on ekasi-pay-api, then redeploy the API once so it bootstraps
# the first ops user into ops_admin_users.
#
# Also set FRONTEND_ORIGINS on ekasi-pay-api to include this ops site URL.
